---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Enterprise — SessionFS" activeNav="enterprise" description="Self-hosted SessionFS on Kubernetes. Your data stays on your infrastructure.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-5 relative noise">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans';">Deploy anywhere.<br>Control everything.</h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Self-hosted Kubernetes deployment with Helm. Your data stays on your infrastructure. Enterprise-tested on AWS EKS.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16">
        <div class="glass p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Self-hosted deployment</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Deploy to any Kubernetes cluster — AWS EKS, GCP GKE, Azure AKS, or on-prem.</p><code class="block text-sm p-3 rounded" style="background: #0a0c10; color: #3ddc84; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">helm install sessionfs ./charts/sessionfs</code></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Data sovereignty</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Your bucket, your database, your infrastructure. Session data never leaves your network.</p><p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">S3, GCS, or local PVC. PostgreSQL (RDS, Cloud SQL, or built-in).</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">AI governance</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Complete audit trail of every AI agent action. LLM Judge V2 with severity-classified findings.</p><p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">Auto-audit on sync or PR/MR. Audit history with model comparison.</p></div>
        <div class="glass p-6"><h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Your LLM gateway</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Bring your own LLM — Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint.</p><p class="text-sm" style="color: #9ca3af;">LiteLLM, vLLM, Ollama, Azure OpenAI all supported.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="glass p-8 text-center max-w-lg mx-auto"><h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Talk to us</h3><p class="text-sm mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Self-hosted deployment, HIPAA compliance, SAML SSO, SLA, and dedicated support.</p><a href="mailto:enterprise@sessionfs.dev?subject=SessionFS%20Enterprise" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold rounded-lg px-7 py-3 hover:brightness-110 transition" style="background: #4f9cf7;">Contact Enterprise Sales</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
